God can bring purpose out of pain.

00:37:54.124 --> 00:37:56.787
He can bring meaning out of chaos.

00:37:58.089 --> 00:38:10.002
For we know this, that God causes all things to work together for good to those who love Him and are called according to His purpose.

00:38:13.378 --> 00:38:16.667
You have been listening to a message from First Baptist Church, Wigital Falls.

00:38:17.269 --> 00:38:25.913
For more information about First Baptist, including gathering times and locations, click the link in the show notes or go to fbcwf.org.

00:38:26.295 --> 00:38:27.538
We'll see you next week.
